{"word":"G626 - ἀπολογέομαι - apologéomai - ap-ol-og-eh'-om-ahee - Answer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπολογέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>apologéomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ap-ol-og-eh'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Answer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மாறுத்தரமாகச் சொல், உத்தரவு சொல், பேசு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to speak so as to absolve oneself, talk oneself off of a charge, to defend oneself, make one's defense"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Middle voice from a compound of <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G3056 - λόγος - lógos - log'-os/3056\">G3056</a>; to give an <i>account</i> (legal <i>plea</i>) of oneself, that is, <i>exculpate</i> (self): - answer (for self), make defence, excuse (self), speak for self."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}